CBRE are pleased to present 39 Neon Street, Sumner for Sale and Lease.

Features of the site include:
- 815sqm Clearspan warehouse
- 355sqm Corporate office over 2 levels
- 112sqm Mezzanine storage area
- Ability to split the site into 2 tenancies
- Over 600sqm concrete hardstand area
- Multiple container height roller doors
- Fully secured facility

Located in Sumner's highly sought after Industrial Estate approximately 15 minutes southwest of the Brisbane CBD. The property offers direct access to major arterials including the Ipswich, Logan and Centenary Motorways and the new Legacy Way Tunnel.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE the Exclusive Agents.

28 Boron Street is located in the rapidly growing precinct of Sumner. Located approximately 14 kilometres West of the Brisbane CBD, this freestanding site gives any occupant direct access to the Centenary Highway and adjoin arterials including the Ipswich and Logan Motorway.

This freestanding facility offers the following features:
- 2,194sqm* Functional warehouse
- 318sqm* Corporate office over two levels
- Access via 6 containers height roller doors
- Ample power onsite
- Dual street crossover access
- Hardstand area at front and rear

*Approx.

For further information or to arrange your inspection, please contact Exclusive Agents
Jonathan Blake or Mark Gilbride from CBRE.

This portal frame office warehouse facility, has two levels of fully air-conditioned office space.  The warehouse is clear span and access is via multi container height roller doors.

14km south of the Brisbane CBD, Sumner Park is located adjacent to the Centenary Highway, providing close proximity to the Ipswich Highway & Logan Motorway.

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact CB Richard Ellis agents:
Mark Clifford - 0408 451 848

Well located industrial facility with warehousing applications.  Spine Street is the main feeder road into the Sumner Park Industrial Estate.  This locality provides ease of access to the Centenary Highway, Ipswich Road and Logan Motorway as well as immediate access to the residential population in the Centenary suburbs.

This property offers the ideal solution for any business looking for extra space for the overflow stock in your current facility or warehousing space for any small business.

Major benefits include:

*  Ampler Hardstand and Car parking
*  90sqm office over two levels
*  275sqm warehousing space
*  Two container height roller doors
*  Good internal height for racking

Given the site's location on Spine Street it allows easy access both in and out of Sumner making this the ideal location for your warehousing needs.

- Totally unaffected by flood
- 938sqm ground floor area
- Additional load bearing mezzanine of 938sqm
- Excellent exposure
- Existing office/showroom areas
- Ample staff and customer parking
- A site with huge potential upside
- Short term income available (up to 12 months)
